claims:
1. A method, comprising:
accessing a distributed ledger comprising an instruction set, wherein the instruction set comprises an instruction set for a polymer production process;
tokenizing the instruction set;
interpreting an instruction set access request;
in response to the instruction set access request, providing a provable access to the instruction set;
providing commands to a production tool of the polymer production process in response to the instruction set access request; and
recording a transaction on the distributed ledger in response to the providing commands to the production tool.
